<h1> Enter your SubsChef Login</h1>
<%= form_tag ({controller: 'sessions', action: 'create', method: 'post'}) %>
    <br>
    <p>Username: <%=text_field_tag 'username'%> </p><br>
    <p>Password: <%= password_field_tag 'password'%> </p><br>
    <%= submit_tag "Log In" %><br>
    <br>
<em>No SubsChef account? You can <%= link_to "sign up here", controller: 'users', action: 'new'%> or login via your <%= link_to "Google account", root_url + "auth/google_oauth2"%>. Joining allows you to contribute your own substitutions and provide other chefs with your own ideas!</em>